attributes.description:
Here's why the Bentley Bentayga 4.0-litre V8 Diesel is a palace on wheels
Most refined 8-cylinder diesel engine developed in the world.
#Bentley has unleashed its very first diesel offering in its history. The Bentayga 4.0-litre twin-turbocharged diesel is mated to an 8-speed automatic transmission. It's good for 320kW and 900Nm of scrumptious torque
The upper cabin is trimmed in Eliade, a tactile technical fabric. Other distinctive characteristics include the rear tail lights illuminating the Bentley B, as well as the side air outlets. The headlights too have the brand name displayed inside the cluster and a bold B on the top of the gear lever.
